<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-1012] runOrder doesn&apos;t seem to have an effect at all for TestNG tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1012</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve tried different runOrders (random, reversealphabetical) with TestNG, but none seems to have an effect at all - tests seem always to be run alphabetically &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
